The initial configuration consists of a cylindrical filament with a hemispherical cap:
```c
event init(t = 0){
  if(!restore (file = dumpFile)){
    // Refine grid near the interface
    refine(x<(h0/2.0)+0.025 && y < hole0+(h0/2.0)+0.025 && level<MAXlevel);

